	  <p>To streamline the animation process for this humanoid model, I rigged the 
	  armature and applied inverse kinematics (IK) to constrain the elbow and knee joints,
	  enabling me to create the efficient walk cycle seen above.</p>
	  <br>
	  <br>
	  
